race.comment: THROTTLE RESPONSE (13) has been right in the finish at the past four efforts and must be respected out of the champion Waller stable. A couple of key scratchings help and rates a leading contender against this line-up. EVELYN MAY (11) looks ready for the step-up in trip now and maps ideally for this from gate two. In the mix. LIVALITTLE (14) will be rock-hard fit after four runs back and may trouble the judge with any luck in running. SAN GABRIEL (7) is a winner around this circuit and only needs some favours from the wide draw to be playing a role in the outcome. MANNERHEIM (5) has a solid record here at this circuit and may earn some minor money.
